data.description: This adorable brick patio home has 2 bedroom 2 bath and is located in Central Montgomery. The main living area has ample room for small gatherings and families. It is move-in ready! It has new wood floors throughout, new windows, and the roof is new. A nice wooden privacy fence with a locked gate and a patio to be able to entertain friends/family. This lovely home would be great for a single person, a young family, or a military family. Please schedule your showings today.
